### **4. 22_StreamLineMatrix**  
**Description:**  
A scrolling live graph for real-time numeric data streams.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamLineMatrix - Live Metric Visualizer

StreamLineMatrix displays incoming numeric values in a smooth, real-time chart that supports multiple data series.

## Features
- Realtime chart with scroll  
- Matplotlib-based  
- Adjustable refresh rate  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/22_StreamLineMatrix.git
cd 22_StreamLineMatrix
python visualize.py
